description: Join us on Thursday, December 5th, 2024, for a delightful evening of connection, relaxation, and nourishment for the mind, body, and soul! We're hosting a special event featuring the best of both worlds: an exciting game night followed by a serene kirtan meditation session. First up, let your competitive spirit soar as you engage in a variety of classic and modern games with friends and fellow participants. Laugh, strategize, and bond over friendly competition in an atmosphere filled with laughter and camaraderie. After the exhilarating game session, immerse yourself in the blissful tranquility of kirtan meditation. Led by experienced practitioners, this ancient practice involves chanting sacred mantras accompanied by soothing music. Allow the rhythmic melodies to guide you into a state of deep relaxation and inner peace. Experience the profound joy and harmony that arise from connecting with yourself and the community through the power of sound and meditation. And to top off the evening, indulge in a sumptuous feast of delectable, nourishing food, provided free for all attendees. Savor the flavors of wholesome dishes that delight the senses and replenish your energy after a fulfilling night of games and meditation. Whether you're seeking fun and excitement or inner peace and spiritual upliftment, our game night and kirtan meditation event promises an unforgettable experience for all. Mark your calendars and join us for an evening of joy, connection, and holistic well-being on Thursday, December 5th!
name: Game Night

description: Come eat snacks and watch Your Name, the 2016 Makoto Shinkai classic! "An emotionally intense, unforgettable viewing experience, filled with 'coming-of-age' fun and spiritual longings. Showcasing Makoto Shinkai’s talent for presenting emotional connections, fully-fledged characters and breathtakingly beautiful, detailed animation, Your Name is a romantic story of an accidental body-swap between country girl Mitsuha and city boy Taki, who, in reality, have never met. Both are high-school students who experience the usual teenagers’ problems and daily ups and downs. However, one day they start to switch bodies back and forth between each other through dreams. Through this experience, Mitsuha and Taki learn many interesting things about themselves, the opposite sex and human, emotional connections." - Diana Tuova, Spotlight on Film
name: JVCA Your Name Movie Night
